abstract: Stocks fall as negotiations between Greece and its creditors continue to remain unresolved.
lead_paragraph: Stocks moved lower as negotiations between Greece and its lenders dragged on and investors become less hopeful that a deal would be reached soon.

headline.main: Market Heads Lower, Erasing Gains for the Week
headline.print_headline: Uncertainty on Greece Helps Wipe Out Week’s Gains

snippet: Stocks moved lower as negotiations between Greece and its lenders dragged on and investors become less hopeful that a deal would be reached soon.
